query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) as total_contacts,
  COUNT(DISTINCT cp.id) as total_phones,
  COUNT(DISTINCT ce.id) as total_emails
FROM properties p
LEFT JOIN contacts c ON p.id = c.propertyId
LEFT JOIN contactPhones cp ON c.id = cp.contactId
LEFT JOIN contactEmails ce ON c.id = ce.contactId
WHERE p.listName = 'Rolando';
